Usage: set_annotated_glitch [-help] [-port <string>] [-vh_glitch <string>]
                            [-vho_glitch <string>] [-view <string>]
                            [-vl_glitch <string>] [-vlu_glitch <string>]

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
-port <string>          # port names on which need to apply glitches
                        # (string, optional)
-vh_glitch <string>     # list of VH glitch wave points (string, optional)
-vho_glitch <string>    # list of VHO glitch wave points (string, optional)
-view <string>          # list of view names (string, optional)
-vl_glitch <string>     # list of VL glitch wave points (string, optional)
-vlu_glitch <string>    # list of VLU glitch wave points (string, optional)